    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pure mechanical connection, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been proactively maintained, including essential subframe reinforcement and a recent shim-and-bucket valve clearance adjustment to ensure the 8,000 RPM redline remains crisp. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its mileage, the suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded bushings, offering the balanced handling and communicative steering rack enthusiasts demand. A mechanically robust example ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
