    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This well-maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and comfort for its next owner. The exterior retains a deep, attractive shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front bumper reflect its honest road history. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space; the upholstery is clean and smoke-free, showing only light natural creasing on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is in solid shape, with a smooth-idling engine and a responsive transmission that shifts through gears effortlessly. All interior electronics, including the infotainment and climate control, are fully operational. It has been kept up to date with regular oil changes and inspections, ensuring it is ready for the road immediately. This is a dependable, high-quality choice for anyone seeking a vehicle that has been cared for properly.",
      "price": 34500.0,
