    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It's been a fantastic ride and is still in really great shape, ready to take you wherever you need to go! It drives smoothly and has been well-loved, so it's perfect for someone who wants a reliable vehicle that's ready for the road today. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner very happy. Drop me a message if you'd like to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 34500.0,
