      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This chassis has been proactively maintained with a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with precision, sending power through the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry is preserved via refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, ensuring optimal damping rates and turn-in response. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with age, the powertrain remains robust, leak-free, and delivers a visceral, analog driving experience. Recent fluid analysis confirms excellent engine health.",
